+DepthBound ==
+    Len(state) <= MaxDepth
 
-EnvelopeLaw2 ==
-    /\ \A i \in DOMAIN state:
+InputBound ==
+    \A i \in DOMAIN state:
         state[i] \in AllowedInputs
 
+HistoryFinite ==
+    IsFiniteSet(DOMAIN state)
+
+EnvelopeBudget ==
+    Len(state) <= MaxEnvelope
+
+InEnvelope ==
+    /\ DepthBound
+    /\ InputBound
+    /\ HistoryFinite
+    /\ EnvelopeBudget
+
+\* Backward-compatible aliases
+EnvelopeLaw1 == DepthBound
+EnvelopeLaw2 == InputBound
+Envelope == InEnvelope
+
